        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="&#x5B89;&#x88DD;"><a href="#&#x5B89;&#x88DD;" class="headerlink" title="&#x5B89;&#x88DD;"></a>&#x5B89;&#x88DD;</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo init [folder]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x6C92;&#x6709;&#x6307;&#x5B9A;&#xFF0C;&#x6703;&#x5728;&#x76EE;&#x524D;&#x8CC7;&#x6599;&#x593E;&#x5EFA;&#x7ACB;&#x7DB2;&#x7AD9;</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="&#x65B0;&#x589E;&#x6587;&#x7AE0;"><a href="#&#x65B0;&#x589E;&#x6587;&#x7AE0;" class="headerlink" title="&#x65B0;&#x589E;&#x6587;&#x7AE0;"></a>&#x65B0;&#x589E;&#x6587;&#x7AE0;</h1><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> &lt;postName&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="&#x7522;&#x751F;&#x975C;&#x614B;&#x6A94;&#x6848;"><a href="#&#x7522;&#x751F;&#x975C;&#x614B;&#x6A94;&#x6848;" class="headerlink" title="&#x7522;&#x751F;&#x975C;&#x614B;&#x6A94;&#x6848;"></a>&#x7522;&#x751F;&#x975C;&#x614B;&#x6A94;&#x6848;</h1><p>&#x6703;&#x7522;&#x751F; public &#x76EE;&#x9304;&#xFF0C;&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x57F7;&#x884C; <code>hexo deploy</code> &#x90E8;&#x7F72;&#xFF0C;&#x5C31;&#x6703;&#x5C07;&#x9019;&#x500B;&#x76EE;&#x9304;&#x5E95;&#x4E0B;&#x7684;&#x5167;&#x5BB9;&#x4E0A;&#x50B3;&#x3002;</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">&#x6216;</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="&#x555F;&#x52D5;&#x672C;&#x6A5F;&#x4F3A;&#x670D;&#x5668;"><a href="#&#x555F;&#x52D5;&#x672C;&#x6A5F;&#x4F3A;&#x670D;&#x5668;" class="headerlink" titl