        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="&#x5B89;&#x88DD;-Vue-Cli"><a href="#&#x5B89;&#x88DD;-Vue-Cli" class="headerlink" title="&#x5B89;&#x88DD; Vue Cli"></a>&#x5B89;&#x88DD; Vue Cli</h1><p>&#x8AB2;&#x7A0B;&#x662F;&#x4EE5; vue-cli 2 &#x7684;&#x7248;&#x672C;&#xFF0C;&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x662F;&#x9019;&#x500B;&#x7248;&#x672C;&#xFF0C;&#x53EF;&#x4EE5;&#x57F7;&#x884C;&#x4EE5;&#x4E0B;&#xFF1A;</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vue init webpack &lt;project name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span id="more"></span><p>&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x4F60;&#x8DDF;&#x6211;&#x4E00;&#x6A23;&#x88DD;&#x4E86; vue cli3 &#xFF0C;&#x53EF;&#x4EE5;&#x4F7F;&#x7528; vue create &lt;&#x5C08;&#x6848;&#x540D;&gt;&#xFF0C;&#x5B89;&#x88DD;&#x6642;&#x53EF;&#x9078;&#x64C7; vue 2 &#x7248;&#x672C;</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vue create &lt;project name&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">// &#x57F7;&#x884C;</span><br><span class="line">npm run serve</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x8A3B;&#xFF1A;<code>npm run dev</code> &#x8DDF; <code>npm run serve</code> &#x53EA;&#x662F;&#x5728; package.json &#x88E1;&#x7684;&#x540D;&#x7A31;&#x4E0D;&#x540C;&#x800C;&#x5DF2;</p><h1 id="&#x5B89;&#x88DD;-Bootstrap-node-sass-sass-loader"><a href="#&#x5B89;&#x88DD;-Bootstrap-node-sass-sass-loader" class="headerlink" title="&#x5B89;&#x88DD; Bootstrap node-sass sass-loader"></a>&#x5B89;&#x88DD; Bootstrap node-sass sass-loader</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install bootstrap node-sass sass-loader --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x6E2C;&#x8A66; scss &#x6709;&#x6C92;&#x6709;&#x88DD;&#x597D;</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><figcaption><span>app.vue</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;style lang=<span class="string">&quot;scss&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  $color: black;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  body {</span><br><span class="line">    background-color: $color;</span><br><span class="line">  }</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>style&#x88E1;&#x6539;&#x7528; @import &#x65B9;&#x5F0F;&#x5F15;&#x5165; BS&#xFF0C;&#x653E;&#x5165; BS HTML &#x5143;&#x4EF6;&#x770B;&#x6548;&#x679C;</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;template&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;div id=<span class="string">&quot;app&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- &#x8981;&#x986F;&#x793A;&#x7684;&#x5167;&#x5BB9;&#x4E00;&#x5B9A;&#x8981;&#x653E;&#x5728; #app &#x88E1;&#x9762; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div id=<span class="string">&quot;nav&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;router-link to=<span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>&gt;Home&lt;/router-link&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      |</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;router-link to=<span class="string">&quot;/about&quot;</span>&gt;About&lt;/router-link&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;router-view/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;card&quot;</span> style=<span class="string">&quot;width: 18rem;&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;div <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;card-body&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;h5 <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;card-title&quot;</span>&gt;Card title&lt;/h5&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;p <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="string">&quot;card-text&quot;</span>&gt;Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk <span class="keyword">of</span> the card<span class="string">&apos;s</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">          content.&lt;/p&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-primary&quot;&gt;Go somewhere&lt;/a&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">      &lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;!-- &#x8981;&#x986F;&#x793A;&#x7684;&#x5167;&#x5BB9;&#x4E00;&#x5B9A;&#x8981;&#x653E;&#x5728; #app &#x88E1;&#x9762; --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">  &lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;/template&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;style lang=&quot;scss&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">@import &quot;~bootstrap/scss/bootstrap&quot;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;/style&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x5728; HelloWorld.vue &#x4E0A;&#x6709; scoped &#x9650;&#x5236;&#x6A23;&#x5F0F;&#x53EA;&#x80FD;&#x5728;&#x8A72;&#x5143;&#x4EF6;&#x4E0A;</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;style scoped lang=<span class="string">&quot;scss&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="install-axios"><a href="#install-axios" class="headerlink" title="install axios"></a>install axios</h1><p>url: <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/vue-axios">https://www.npmjs.com/package/vue-axios</a></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install --save axios vue-axios</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>at main.js import</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><figcaption><span>main.js</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> axios <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&apos;axios&apos;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> VueAxios <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&apos;vue-axios&apos;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// use</span></span><br><span class="line">Vue.use(VueAxios, axios)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x4F60;&#x4E0D;&#x5C0F;&#x5FC3;&#x5B89;&#x88DD;&#x4E86; es-lint &#xFF0C;&#x904B;&#x884C;&#x6642;&#x51FA;&#x73FE;&#x63D0;&#x793A;&#x61C9;&#x4FEE;&#x6B63;&#x932F;&#x8AA4;&#xFF0C;&#x53EF;&#x4EE5;&#x7528;&#x4EE5;&#x4E0B;&#x6307;&#x4EE4;&#x67E5;&#x627E;&#x4E3B;&#x8981;&#x932F;&#x8AA4;&#x7684;&#x5730;&#x65B9;&#x3002;</p><p>&#x986F;&#x793A;&#x4E3B;&#x8981;&#x932F;&#x8AA4;&#xFF08;&#x5FFD;&#x7565;prettier&#xFF09;</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm run lint --fix</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; vue-shop@<span class="number">0.1</span><span class="number">.0</span> lint</span><br><span class="line">&gt; vue-cli-service lint</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">error: <span class="string">&apos;HelloWorld&apos;</span> is defined but never used (no-unused-vars) at src/App.vue:<span class="number">29</span>:<span class="number">8</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">27</span> |</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">28</span> | &lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&gt; <span class="number">29</span> | <span class="keyword">import</span> HelloWorld <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;./components/HelloWorld&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     |        ^</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">30</span> |</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">31</span> | <span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> {</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">32</span> |   name: <span class="string">&quot;App&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span> error found.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x4FEE;&#x6B63;&#x932F;&#x8AA4;&#x5F8C;&#x6C92;&#x6709;&#x554F;&#x984C;&#xFF0C;&#x5247;&#x6703;&#x51FA;&#x73FE;&#x2026;</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm run lint --fix</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&gt; vue-shop@<span class="number">0.1</span><span class="number">.0</span> lint</span><br><span class="line">&gt; vue-cli-service lint</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> DONE  No lint errors found!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>&#x4F7F;&#x7528; axios</p><figure class="highlight jsx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> {</span><br><span class="line">  name: <span class="string">&quot;App&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function"><span class="title">created</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span> {    <span class="comment">// &#x6211;&#x4E0D;&#x5C0F;&#x5FC3;&#x6253;&#x6210; create() &#x6E2C;&#x8A66;&#x534A;&#x5929;&#x624D;&#x627E;&#x5230;&#x539F;&#x56E0;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">this</span>.$http.get(<span class="string">&quot;https://randomuser.me/api/&quot;</span>).then(<span class="function">(<span class="params">response</span>) =&gt;</span> {</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">console</span>.log(response);</span><br><span class="line">    });</span><br><span class="line">  },</span><br><span class="line">};</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="&#x589E;&#x52A0;&#x81EA;&#x8A02;-API-&#x8DEF;&#x5F91;"><a href="#&#x589E;&#x52A0;&#x81EA;&#x8A02;-API-&#x8DEF;&#x5F91;" class="headerlink" title="&#x589E;&#x52A0;&#x81EA;&#x8A02; API &#x8DEF;&#x5F91;"></a>&#x589E;&#x52A0;&#x81EA;&#x8A02; API &#x8DEF;&#x5F91;</h1><p>&#x5C31;&#x662F;&#x6211;&#x5011;&#x7533;&#x8ACB;&#x7684;&#x81EA;&#x8A02; API &#x8DEF;&#x5F91;&#x3002;&#x8AB2;&#x7A0B;&#x8AAA;&#x8981;&#x4FEE;&#x6539; config\ &#x76EE;&#x9304;&#x4E0B;&#x7684;&#x8A2D;&#x5B9A;&#x6A94;&#xFF0C;&#x589E;&#x52A0; API &#x5E38;&#x6578;&#xFF0C;&#x4F46;&#x4F7F;&#x7528;&#x65B0;&#x7248;&#x672C; Vue Cli3 &#x5728;&#x6839;&#x76EE;&#x9304;&#x4E2D;&#x5DF2;&#x7D93;&#x6C92;&#x6709; config &#x3001;build &#x7B49;&#x76EE;&#x9304;&#xFF0C;&#x5982;&#x679C;&#x8981;&#x52A0;&#x5E38;&#x6578;&#xFF0C;&#x8981;&#x5728;&#